OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPensions tax cut is wrong  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpriority, Labour says      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Labour has said it would reverse plans 
OL,6, to scrap a #1m cap on how much workers 
OL,7, can accumulate in their pensions       
OL,8, savings before paying extra tax.       
OL,10,FShadow chancellor Rachel Reeves said   
OL,11,Fthe move, announced in the Budget, was 
OL,12,Fa "tax cut for the top 1%" and "the    
OL,13,Fwrong priority, at the wrong time".    
OL,15,FThe government said the policy was     
OL,16,Faimed at stopping doctors and other    
OL,17,Fprofessionals retiring early.          
OL,19,FThe plans are part of a wider drive to 
OL,20,Fget people back to work.               
